summary: This document is a correspondence from T-Mobile / MetroPCS indicating their inability to respond to a legal demand regarding a specific target telephone number. The reason provided is that the number is not associated with any subscriber during the specified date range.
keyFacts: T-Mobile / MetroPCS was unable to respond to a legal demand.
The target telephone number was not associated with a T-Mobile or MetroPCS subscriber.
The date of the correspondence is June 1, 2019.
